  <div class="pulse-wrap">
    <div class="audit-grid">
      <div class="audit-item"><strong>Branding</strong>Logo GR · Greece RE · was Mexico shell on several niche sites — fixed in this report.</div>
      <div class="audit-item"><strong>Sitemap vs API</strong>Live sitemap 113 URLs · Google API log 113 · gap 0.</div>
