      <div class="pulse-kpi"><div class="kpi-label">Avg. CTR</div><div class="kpi-val">—</div><div class="kpi-sub">CTR sprint when 50+ imp/query</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="insight"><strong>Quick wins pipeline (when data arrives):</strong> Priority URLs — <code>/guides/greece-property-investment-guide/</code>, <code>/guides/greece-golden-visa-property-2026/</code>, <code>/guides/can-foreigners-buy-property-greece/</code>, <code>/guides/athens-property-investment-guide/</code>, <code>/compare/greece-vs-portugal-property-investment/</code>. Pages at pos 8–15 with 50+ impressions → expand FAQ + retitle for CTR. Monitor via <code>search-console-greek-invest</code> MCP.</div>
    <p style="font-size:11px;color:#a8a29e;text-align:center;margin-top:16px;">Updated 19 June 2026 via GSC API · EN site — never Yandex</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section-title">Analytics — GA4</div>
